description: More than 240 migrants test positive at the new Lesbos camp built after the old one burnt down.
title: Lesbos: Hundreds test positive for Covid-19 after migrant camp fire

maintext: "We can't close our eyes and turn our backs and walk away from them," Tima Kurdi, who spoke at the Berlin demonstration, said. "People are people, no matter where we come from."
